value.name: Lambda Herculis - Wikipedia
value.snippet: Lambda Herculis (λ Herculis. abbreviated Lambda Her, λ Her), formally named Maasym / ˈ m eɪ ə s ɪ m /, is a star in the constellation of Hercules. From parallax measurements taken during the Gaia mission, it is approximately 393 light-years from the Sun. Nomenclature. λ Herculis (Latinised to Lambda Herculis) is the star's Bayer designation.

value.name: Maasym (Lambda Herculis) Star Facts (Distance, Colour & more)
value.snippet: Hercules Maasym Maasym (Lambda Herculis) Maasym is a Giant Star that is located in the constellation of Hercules, the Warrior. Based on the spectral type (K3IIIvar) of the star, the Maasym colour is orange to red . Maasym is the traditional/proper name for the star whilst Lambda Herculis is the Bayer classification for the star.

value.name: Lambda Herculis – Wikipedia
value.snippet: λ Herculis (Lambda Herculis, kurz λ Her) ist ein Stern mit einer scheinbaren visuellen Helligkeit von 4,4 mag. Er ist knapp 400 Lichtjahre entfernt und in Richtung des Sternbilds Hercules gelegen. Der Stern trägt den historischen Eigennamen Maasym , der sich von arabisch معصم (DMG miʿṣam), ‚Handgelenk‘, ableitet.

value.name: Lambda Herculis — Wikipédia
value.snippet: Lambda Herculis (λ Herculis, abrégée λ Her), appelée également Maasym [7], est une étoile de la constellation d'Hercule. Elle est à environ 385 années-lumière de la Terre. Noms traditionnels. Elle porte le nom traditionnel Maasym, qui signifie « poignet ».

value.name: Lambda Herculis - Wikiwand
value.snippet: Lambda Herculis é uma estrela na direção da constelação de Hercules. Possui uma ascensão reta de 17h 30m 44.30s e uma declinação de +26° 06′ 38.2″. Sua magnitude aparente é igual a 4.41. Considerando sua distância de 367 anos-luz em relação à Terra, sua magnitude absoluta é igual a −0.85. Pertence à classe espectral K3IIIvar.

value.name: Hercules Constellation Stars – Astrology King
value.snippet: Hercules, the figure on bended knee and called by the Greek name of Engonasin, about whose origin no certainty prevails. Of this constellation is begotten the desertion, craftiness, and deceit characteristic of its children, and from it comes the thug who terrorizes the heart of the city.
